# Brickbase Coding Standards

## Structure

- `apps/web` – Next.js app (property assets trading UI)
- `apps/mcp` – MCP server for AI/automation
- `libs/contracts` – Solidity smart contracts (Hardhat)
- `libs/abi` – Shared ABIs (`@brickbase/abi`)
- `libs/shared-config` – Chain config, env

## Conventions

- Use `@brickbase/abi` for contract ABIs in web and mcp
- Contract addresses via `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` env vars
- Nx targets: `nx run web:build`, `nx run contracts:compile`, `nx run mcp:serve`
